getKamNodeCandidates

public List<Integer> getKamNodeCandidates(Kam.KamNode example)
                                   throws SQLException
Retrieves candidate kam node ids that contain global parameters found in the example kam node.

For instance, given a kam with the following nodes:

  • complex(p(1), g(2))
  • p(1)
  • g(2)
  • r(2)
  • act(r(2))
Providing the complex(p(1), g(2)) kam node will yield ids for the following similar kam nodes:
  • p(1)
  • g(2)
  • r(2)
  • act(r(2))

Specified by:
getKamNodeCandidates in interface KAMStoreDao
Parameters:
example - Kam.KamNode, the kam node to retrieve similar matches on, which cannot be null or have a null id
Returns:
the ids of kam nodes containing similar global parameters
Throws:
SQLException - Thrown if a SQL error occurred retrieving similar node matches
